                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150405-13-victim173 t18150405-13-viclabel71"></join>, did make an assault, and that they, with a certain gun loaded with gunpowder and leaden shot, feloniously did shoot off and discharge at the said 
