                  , on her head did strike, penetrate, and wound, thereby giving to her on the head two mortal wounds, of which she languished from the 7th of March, until the 18th of March, and then died; and so the Jurors say, that they, the aforesaid prisoners, her, the said 
                     <persName id="t18150405-13-person176">
                        Jane 
                        Watson
                     <interp inst="t18150405-13-person176" type="surname" value="Watson"></interp>
